These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
City: san-francisco, prague
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, november
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is not the person traveling to prague##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | prague   | san-francisco  |
| Sport   | april | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, azure
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, epic
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is not the person who likes azure##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | white | azure      |
| Pet    | romance  | epic |

 #################################

 
